data.title: Istiklal Street Walk in Beyoğlu
data.meta_description: Ready to take a walk along one of the liveliest, most colorful streets in Istanbul? Join your guide for a fun and insightful tour of İstiklal - home to many historic buildings, fancy hotels, apartment buildings and more. Then it's time for another history lesson, as you explore the famous Beyoğlu district.
data.text:
Ready to take a walk along one of the liveliest, most colorful streets in Istanbul? Join your guide for a fun and insightful tour of İstiklal - home to many historic buildings, fancy hotels, apartment buildings and more. Then it's time for another history lesson, as you explore the famous Beyoğlu district.

What's included

3.5-hour walking tour of Istiklal Street and the district of Beyoğlu

English-speaking guide providing commentary and insights

What's excluded
